right</span></a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-lg\">\n<!-- Course Card 1 -->\n<div class=\"bg-surface rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all overflow-hidden group\">\n<div class=\"relative h-40 overflow-hidden\">\n<img class=\"w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform group-hover:scale-105\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDcW-HO-WKd_ZrjwvkSd8FdvlDWBbILZ0lshT1DEqDcqywgSIZLLt-ioJiHJ-jmQtkXKj_CHgbz8iQcwrZaV62X87VbO6t0ybGfu7Q-cJd22JUbpLKRiRj__3zO8S68nJkJ26OUA30ArayX2i4n5zvoKqHEKmYW0JMjH7EREj9Acczhysyr4wu7yDrU_k8z0_p9U41fhWqjz8DkyzzdEcSxwmwXVy7LpjolfPRa3eMqkQEkNxunqwTVJlWyXcryk1r3UUZLMSPaeN0\"/>\n<div class=\"absolute top-2 right-2 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-md text-white text-[10px] px-2 py-1 rounded-md uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\">Advanced</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-md space-y-md\">\n<h5 class=\"font-headline-sm text-base text-on-surface line-clamp-1\">Industrial 5-Axis CNC Machining: Precision Process Optimization</h5>\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-on-surface-variant font-label-sm\">\n<span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]\">schedule</span> 4.5 hours</span>\n<span class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[16px]\">signal_cellular_alt</span> Difficulty: Intermediate</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"space-y-1.5\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between text-[11px] font-bold text-on-surface-variant\">\n<span class=\"\">Current Progress</span>\n<span class=\"\">65%</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-full h-1.5 bg-outline-variant rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n<div class=\"bg-primary h-full rounded-full\" style=\"width: 65%;\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Course Card 2 -->\n<div class=\"bg-surface rounded-xl border border-outline-variant shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all overflow-hidden group\">\n<div class=\"relative h-40 overflow-hidden\">\n<im